domain 0.1-0-SNAPSHOT API

Packages
Package
Description
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain
This package contains the core domain logic of the OmniCommunicator.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.exception
This package contains the custom domain exceptions of the OmniCommunicator.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.model
This package contains the entity classes and value objects that make up the domain model of the OmniCommunicator.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.orchestrator
This package contains the classes that coordinate and orchestrate operations between different services of the OmniCommunicator.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.port.inbound
This package contains the interfaces representing the operations that the OmniCommunicator offers to the outside world.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.port.outbound
This package contains the interfaces representing the operations that the OmniCommunicator needs to interact with the outside world.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.service
This package contains the domain service classes of the OmniCommunicator.
br.com.quicula.omnicommunicator.domain.utils
This package contains utility classes for the domain layer of the OmniCommunicator.
